              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: 1. All meals / drinks by guest own expenses 2. Raincoat or umbrella recommended 3. Please bring your own umbrella or raincoat in case of rain, as the tour will proceed as scheduled, even in wet weather conditions 4. This tour is not private and may include other guests 5. No eating or drinking is allowed inside the car/van/buses. Food can easily become messy, or someone might bump into you, having you spill your drink or squash your food, letting it fall to the floor. 6. This SIC itinerary vehicle is arranged according to the number of participants on the day (car/van/bus) 7. Please make sure your mobile phone number is active and able to contacted during the travel period 8. It is recommended that you make preparations to prevent if you have motion sickness, so as not to affect your pleasant journey. 9. Please keep your belongings and try not to bring valuables, you will be responsible for all damages and loss."
